{"tid":1531893,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"黑衫行動 黑衫運動 黑衫抗爭 黑衫潮流","createTime":"2019-09-02T11:06:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-02T15:04:40.000Z","uid":55759,"like":91,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":39,"replies":[{"pid":"ef851f7c1693d8747881858b18df0e957ebc85a8","tid":1531893,"uid":55759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:06:50.000Z","msg":"同埋大家真係要醒覺<br />\n著黑衫唔犯法<br />\n戴口罩唔犯法<br />\n戴頭盔唔犯法<br />\n戴防毒面具都唔犯法<br />\n<br />\n千其唔好因為做咗呢啲嘢有虧心事嘅感覺<br />\n應該將呢樣嘢成為主流<br />\n成為大家作為對抗極權政府嘅一個表<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一個破解黑警亂捉黑衣方法<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/agidsgV\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/agidsgV</a><br />\n#15 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n而家社會瀰漫住著黑衫已經有罪嘅風氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但呢個係對家嘅<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">心理圈套</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果你連出街著黑衫都驚，有心虛淆底嘅感覺<br />\n不如你聽班狗話<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">驚就唔好出街</span></strong></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>全民黑衫 正式啓動 </strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee0d0ef3f110a46b211151d3f218636226a4377e","tid":1531893,"uid":55759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:07:39.000Z","msg":"文宣組唔該<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0eb68dfc985b8a38b2cfb2504ddede75fdc91e57","tid":1531893,"uid":55759,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:09:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">全民皆黑 以表決心</span></span>"},{"pid":"1e87b9a157ce5911edb4cf3ce1d741e103cd4480","tid":1531893,"uid":212182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:10:09.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"e1d931c88b641be54b439e2dcca7719db7f41363","tid":1531893,"uid":196861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:10:49.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0b207d06ccd0e3fe75f5f022d128e9829afee0e7","tid":1531893,"uid":55759,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-02T11:11:25.000Z","msg":"香港<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">蒙面法</span></span>都未撚有<br />\n你地就連著黑衫都淆撚曬底<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/poin